scores.description:
List of ORES score objects. Each model here was used to score this revision.  Example: {
  "model_name": "awesomeness",
  "model_version": "1.0.1",
  "prediction": ["yes", "mostly"],
  "probability": [
    {"name": "yes",    "value": 0.99},
    {"name": "mostly", "value": 0.90},
    {"name": "hardly", "value": 0.01}
  ]
}
